snippet.title: The Frustrated Gamer
snippet.description:
What is going on everybody?! I am Brandon AKA The Frustrated Gamer and welcome to my gaming YouTube channel! I play a wide variety of PC games including Baldi's Basics, Solar Smash, Five Night's At Freddy's, Minecraft and much more! 

- NEW VIDEO EVERY MORNING!
